field.value:
In addition to {{Configure()}} and {{ConfigureFor<SomeType>()}} a more generic method should be provided to allow custom predicate to determine if configuration should be applied, so for example we only attach security interceptor to types with an attibute.

{code lang=java}
void ConfigureIf(Predicate<ComponentRegistration> condition, Action<ComponentRegistration> action);

void ConfigureIf(Predicate<ComponentRegistration> condition, Action<ComponentRegistration> actionWhenTrue, Action<ComponentRegistration> actionWhenFalse);
{code}
